@startuml Sequence_UC05
title UC-05: Kelola Bahan Baku

actor "Bagian Inventori" as User
participant "Halaman Bahan Baku\n(livewire/material)" as View
participant "Material\\Form\n(Livewire)" as Component
participant "Material Model" as MaterialModel
participant "MaterialDetail Model" as DetailModel
database "Database" as DB

User -> View: Membuka /bahan-baku
View -> Component: mount()
Component -> DB: SELECT materials WITH units
DB --> Component: Collection<Material>
Component --> View: Render daftar bahan baku beserta stok

== Tambah Bahan Baku ==
User -> View: Klik Tambah lalu isi form\n(nama, satuan, harga beli, gambar) lalu simpan
View -> Component: save()
Component -> Component: validate(['name'=>'required|unique',\n'image'=>'nullable|mimes:jpg,jpeg,png|max:2048'])
alt Validasi gagal
  Component --> View: Pesan kesalahan
  View --> User: Tampilkan error
else Berhasil
  Component -> MaterialModel: Material::create([...])
  MaterialModel -> DB: INSERT INTO materials
  DB --> MaterialModel: Material baru
  Component -> DetailModel: MaterialDetail::create(['material_id'=>$id,...])
  DetailModel -> DB: INSERT INTO material_details (satuan & harga utama)
  Component --> View: Notifikasi sukses & daftar diperbarui
end

== Ubah Bahan Baku ==
User -> View: Klik edit, ubah data, lalu simpan
View -> Component: edit($id), save()
Component -> MaterialModel: Material::findOrFail($id)
MaterialModel -> DB: SELECT materials WHERE id = ?
DB --> MaterialModel: Material record
Component -> Component: validate & handle upload gambar baru
Component -> MaterialModel: $material->update([...])
MaterialModel -> DB: UPDATE materials WHERE id = ?

Component -> DetailModel: MaterialDetail::updateOrCreate(['material_id'=>$id], [...])
DetailModel -> DB: UPDATE material_details WHERE material_id = ?

Component -> MaterialModel: Hitung ulang stok & status minimum
MaterialModel -> DB: UPDATE materials SET status = ? WHERE id = ?
Component --> View: Notifikasi sukses

@enduml
